<section 
  class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-navy text-white"
  aria-labelledby="about-snapshot-heading"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 
          id="about-snapshot-heading"
          class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white"
        >
          Rooted in the North Country
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-pretty">
          For over two decades, North Country Realty Group has been the trusted name in Lancaster, NH and throughout the greater North Country region. We're more than real estate agents—we're your neighbors, your friends, and your partners in finding the perfect place to call home.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-pretty">
          From cozy starter homes to sprawling mountain estates, we have the local knowledge and dedication to help you navigate every step of your real estate journey. Our commitment to personalized service and community values sets us apart.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/about"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-8 text-gold hover:text-gold-light font-semibold text-lg transition-colors group"
        >
          Learn More About Us
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560518883-ce09059eeffa?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
            alt="Real estate agents collaborating and discussing property details with clients"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-gold text-navy p-6 rounded-lg shadow-xl hidden sm:block">
          <p class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold">25+</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">Years of Excellence</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
